Package com.github.lucbui.annotations

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Absolute
    If this is present on a field, the offset calculated is absolute, rather than relative.
    AfterRead
    Marks a method to be invoked after it is constructed by a pipeline
    BeforeWrite
    Marks a method to be invoked before it is written by a ReflectionHexWriter
    DataStructure
    Marks an object as a Data Structure.
    DataStructureSize
    Marks a method to be invoked to calculate the size of a Data Structure.
    Offset
    Marks an annotation for an arithmetic string that calculates an offset.
    PointerField
    Defines a PointerField for a structure, which stores an object + a pointer to that object.
